               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1019Actsof">Acts of the Apostles</title>
                     <note>
                        The arrangement of the text is incorrect and some parts are missing. The sequence according to the original arrangement is: 
                        1:9 (<q xml:lang="gez">ወእንዘ፡</q>, on <locus target="#15r" facs="0016"/>) - 2:3 (<q xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡</q>, on <locus target="#16v" facs="0018"/>); 
                        2:38 (<q xml:lang="gez">በስሙ፡</q>, on <locus target="#9r" facs="0010"/>) - 4:30 (<q xml:lang="gez">ወመንክር፡</q>, on <locus target="#14v" facs="0016"/>); 
                        4:30 (<q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡</q>, on <locus target="#1r" facs="0002"/>) - 7:32  (<q xml:lang="gez">ወአምላ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="lost">ከ፡</t:supplied>
                        </q>, on <locus target="#8v" facs="0010"/>); 
                        18:27 (<q xml:lang="gez">ጸሐፋ፡</q>, on <locus target="#17r" facs="0018"/>) - 26:5 (<q xml:lang="gez">አበ<t:supplied xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="lost">ዊነ፡</t:supplied>
                        </q>, on <locus target="#34v" facs="0037"/>). 
                        Numerous corrections and additions were inserted by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9286Tasfase">Tasfā Ṣǝyon</persName>, 
                        as well as of numbers indicating the pages of <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/8UWD3FCM"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Petrus1548Test"/><title level="m">Testamentum Novum: Cum Epistola Pauli Ad Hebreos tantum, cum concordantijs Evangelistarum Eusebii &amp; numeratione omnium verborum eorundem. Missale cum benedictione incensi cerae et c. Alphabetum in lingua ግእዝ፡ gheez, idest libera quia a nulla alia originem duxit, &amp; vulgo dicitur Chaldea, Quae omnia Fr. Petrus Ethyops auxilio piorum sedente Paulo. III. Pont. MAx. &amp; Claudio illius regni Imperatore imprimi curavit</title><author><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Petrus Ethyops</t:name></author><pubPlace>Romae</pubPlace><publisher>Impensis Petri Comos Ethiopis, Valerius Doricus</publisher><date>1548</date><note type="url">https://books.google.de/books?id=KPNa9Mc5gjYC</note><citedRange unit="fol">133-157</citedRange></bibl>. 
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
          
